721664f-a.folder: Monroe Street & Catherine Street, Manhattan, NY
721664f-a.text:
Monroe Street, at, adjoining and east of the N.E. corner of Catherine Street. Also shown on the left is the east side of Catherine Street, north from and including Monroe Street. On the N.E. corner of Catherine and Monroe Streets, is the Roman Catholic Church of San Giuseppe. In the foreground appears the excavation for Knickerbocker Village.
March 6, 1934.
P. L. Sperr.
